ostId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKblIxZGlhVkZ2T0ZWeWRGSnlUeTEyY1ROMVNIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKblIxZGlhVkZ2T0ZWeWRGSnlUeTEyY1ROMVNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c700455a8395:0xda6710e720550ee6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlYNaRQDHwoAR5g5VIOcQZ9o/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21abFpGcE1WalprVjNKaU9Fd3lVek5VWDJGeGVWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "This place is known for quality matcha and specialty flavors. Line went by quickly only waiting 8 minutes out the door. I will say, the atmosphere is nice although, the temperature in here is very HOT. The workers look red and sweaty. I feel so bad for them and that reflects on the way they treat the customers. Please do better for your\nemployees!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is known for quality matcha and specialty flavors. Line went by quickly only waiting 8 minutes out the door. I will say, the atmosphere is nice although, the temperature in here is very HOT. The workers look red and sweaty. I feel so bad for them and that reflects on the way they treat the customers. Please do better for your\nemployees!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Stephanie Marie Vigil", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109452407311395661888/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7kNcYr0vFcVbdvxaDB_NEoOlZvz4fe-F_ojmxvfajMkfQMIrMsg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-01T23:15:40.340188411Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21abFpGcE1WalprVjNKaU9Fd3lVek5VWDJGeGVWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21abFpGcE1WalprVjNKaU9Fd3lVek5VWDJGeGVWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c700455a8395:0xda6710e720550ee6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJlYNaRQDHwoAR5g5VIOcQZ9o/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOeGVGRkdhM2RLTWpSRE16UlBRMFpLWjI4NVJrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The coffee was amazing! We tried a Brown Sugae iced latte with oat milk, a hot Yala latte and the Vanilla Bean latte with oat milk. The Vanilla Bean latte was my favorite of the three! Perfect blend of sweetness to the coffee. The 2 hot latte’s cost about the same but somehow the Vanilla Bean was the larger portion of the two. Will definitely come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The coffee was amazing! We tried a Brown Sugae iced latte with oat milk, a hot Yala latte and the Vanilla Bean latte with oat milk. The Vanilla Bean latte was my favorite of the three! Perfect blend of sweetness to the coffee. The 2 hot latte’s cost about the same but somehow the Vanilla Bean was the larger portion of the two. Will definitely come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "BB", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106538415784088401498/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1zc2g-glyvzUbrLEDRlh4fif2Vvz4CXIXYWUTbzI0uNk-oQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-05T22:54:20.254870859Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOeGVGRkdhM2RLTWpSRE16UlBRMFpLWjI4NVJrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOeGVGRkdhM2RLTWpSRE16UlBRMFpLWjI4NVJrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c700455a8395:0xda6710e720550ee6"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJlYNaRQDHwoAR5g5VIOcQZ9o/photos/AWCwydjHjFRm1ZkXxGL7zvVfJGjzTeMAx27FtwuDvwWHFx00bt0OJZ_VJouehBY_TkvB0aynMiqDnEYtb3WmWG5y5-3WPYCR60LyIfNQ4eT-tnB1eFnUY_XkAE7qxhlehqyMT1JhnUONMIXCoteyt8dakMcV_aFhOkYpphixxJvqdBrS_r4X5E5XfBe-1SPL_NwKPwTI9uizpnlZBXF4zheTpMyj39VuF9GkhZsET0_Lpph34Dlwt-Ni5ydfHXSF7d1b9bfgKtB2Qa5myPDHMR7EpyEazcOiZ-5qZ1zeZ-ISl6i7byRqmHhbk8uQq_HzNmheGK9ulYbWn